    "description": "Halflings are typically the jolly residents of pastoral shires, or the often-larcenous denizens of towns and cities. Halflings are short in stature, sport hairy feet, and normally profess a deep love for Pipe Weed. Halflings love fine food, fine wine, and abstaining from adventure. Occasionally, a halfling leaves their idyllic life in the countryside, or a life of petty theft in the city, to seek high adventures, often in the company of dwarves and sorcerers."
